    {
      "id": "PopularPost122717",
      "post_content": "Okay guys, the art is simple.  \n  \nIt represents one of Urza's [Power Armor](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Power Armor)'s, probably one belonging to one of the nine titans when they attacked Phyrexia, as you can tell by the darkness and swarms around it.  \n  \nThe power armor also featured in the old art of [Urza's Rage](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Urza's Rage).  \n  \n@OpeeFomenom  \nWhile I agree with you mostly, I would like to say that \"A different artist\" wouldn't change what was depicted. The style designers decide it and send the descri-ption to the artist.  ",
